            "description": "<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\n</p><p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\"> \n\nDiscover our full collection of men’s swim shorts, designed with style and comfort in mind. From classic colours to bold, tropical-prints, our swim shorts feature quick-drying fabrics, breathable mesh or compression linings, adjustable drawstring waists, and practical details like side pockets-ideal for beach days, poolside lounging, or active swims. \nGetting ready to hit the gym or train before a swim? Browse our full range of men’s activewear, including <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/training-tops\" class=\"link text-magenta-500\">training tops</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/sports-shorts\" class=\"link text-magenta-500\">gym shorts</a> and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/socks/style-sports\" class=\"link text-magenta-500\">sports socks</a> to support your feet whilst you work out – perfect with sliders on your way to the pool. Planning your next getaway? Explore our <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/pages/summer-shop\" class=\"link text-magenta-500\">Summer Shop</a> for vacation-ready clothing and accessories. From tropical-print swim shorts to travel-friendly men’s and women’s <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/bamboo-underwear\" class=\"link text-magenta-500\">bamboo boxer shorts</a>– made with breathable, sweat-wicking fabric to keep you cool and comfortable wherever summer takes you. Not sure which pair’s right for you? Our easy size guide and hassle-free returns make finding your fit simple.\n\n</p>\n<br>\n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\n</p><p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\"> \nShop our Swim Shorts today! </p>",
